nnoremap cg# g*``cgN
nnoremap d*   *``dgn
nnoremap d#   *``dgN
nnoremap dg* g*``dgn
nnoremap dg# g*``dgN

" Navigate folds
nnoremap          zf zMzvzz
nnoremap <silent> zj :silent! normal! zc<cr>zjzvzz
nnoremap <silent> zk :silent! normal! zc<cr>zkzvzz[z

